      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "The babies kick us off. CONCERNED (1) will find this a little easier than his second on debut three weeks ago, beaten a nose at the end of 1000m at this track. Likely improver so he is worth following up. MISHANI ADIOS (2) started at big odds on debut last start but ran a bold race, finishing third and beaten 2.5 lengths over 1000m at Sunshine Coast. Will be better with race experience now under the belt is expected to be in the finish. NIFTY'S TREASURE (3) was prominent at the corner and finished third last time over 1000m at this circuit when resuming from a spell, beaten 2.5 lengths. Suitably placed so anticipating a big run again. CRIMSON COMMANDER (8) faced the starter for the first time and finished fifth last start at this venue over 1000m, beaten 4.5 lengths. Should be thereabouts with natural improvement.",
